{
  "videoId": "wviYUDGhie4",
  "language": "en",
  "duration": 213.14,
  "segmentCount": 110,
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.04,
      "text": "If you don't hook people within four seconds"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "start": 2.04,
      "end": 5.61,
      "text": "of starting your video, you're toast."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "start": 5.61,
      "end": 7.61,
      "text": "And all of your hard work on scripts, recording,"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "start": 7.61,
      "end": 9.91,
      "text": "and editing can be thrown out the door."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "start": 9.91,
      "end": 12.19,
      "text": "So today, we're gonna look at five visual hooks"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "start": 12.19,
      "end": 13.51,
      "text": "that you can try in your videos."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "start": 13.51,
      "end": 15.13,
      "text": "These are things you do not say"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "start": 15.13,
      "end": 17.39,
      "text": "at the start of your videos to hook viewers."
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "start": 17.39,
      "end": 19.75,
      "text": "Bonus points, if you can make these a recurring thing"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "start": 19.75,
      "end": 21.11,
      "text": "that makes it easy for viewers"
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "start": 21.11,
      "end": 22.99,
      "text": "to recognize that you made the video."
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "start": 22.99,
      "end": 24.99,
      "text": "My visual hook is this pink fluffy mic"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "start": 24.99,
      "end": 26.67,
      "text": "and my pretty decent background."
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "start": 26.67,
      "end": 28.39,
      "text": "For you, it might be wearing a cap,"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "start": 28.39,
      "end": 29.43,
      "text": "holding your dog,"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "start": 29.43,
      "end": 34.32,
      "text": "or taking a sip of water before you actually start talking."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "start": 34.32,
      "end": 36.32,
      "text": "The first visual hook that you could try"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "start": 36.32,
      "end": 39.04,
      "text": "is to film from an unexpected or weird setting."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "start": 39.04,
      "end": 40.72,
      "text": "This could be filming from your car"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "start": 40.72,
      "end": 42.4,
      "text": "or maybe on a morning walk."
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "start": 42.4,
      "end": 44.12,
      "text": "Just look at this video by Patrick"
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "start": 44.12,
      "end": 45.36,
      "text": "where he films from his car."
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "start": 45.36,
      "end": 49.4,
      "text": "To our N8N workflow, so absurdly inexpensive, super power."
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "start": 49.4,
      "end": 52.0,
      "text": "Or this video by Jay where he's on his morning walk."
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "start": 52.0,
      "end": 54.08,
      "text": "You know, would be a good fit in saying,"
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "start": 54.08,
      "end": 55.8,
      "text": "hey, I don't know if you saw this,"
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "start": 55.8,
      "end": 57.88,
      "text": "but I offer this product or service to this program."
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "start": 57.88,
      "end": 58.72,
      "text": "I think it'd be a great fit."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "start": 58.72,
      "end": 60.52,
      "text": "If you don't wanna do the unexpected setting,"
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "start": 60.56,
      "end": 62.92,
      "text": "at least invest in an aesthetically pleasing background."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "start": 62.92,
      "end": 65.16,
      "text": "That's why I'd rather film here with a set of lamps"
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "start": 65.16,
      "end": 67.6,
      "text": "than in the dark with my lamps off."
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "start": 67.6,
      "end": 69.56,
      "text": "The second visual hook is color."
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "start": 69.56,
      "end": 70.92,
      "text": "Yes, it's that easy."
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "start": 70.92,
      "end": 72.64,
      "text": "You can easily introduce more color"
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "start": 72.64,
      "end": 74.64,
      "text": "in the stuff you wear or in your background."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "start": 74.64,
      "end": 75.96,
      "text": "That's why this shirt does better"
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "start": 75.96,
      "end": 77.56,
      "text": "than this boring gray shirt."
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "start": 77.56,
      "end": 78.88,
      "text": "If you're not gonna go with color,"
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "start": 78.88,
      "end": 81.36,
      "text": "go with something weird or unexpected on your shirts."
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "start": 81.36,
      "end": 82.4,
      "text": "Like our founder Grant,"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "start": 82.4,
      "end": 84.56,
      "text": "whose visual hook is to wear weird t-shirts."
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "start": 84.56,
      "end": 86.84,
      "text": "Here's his hardcore software t-shirt."
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "start": 86.84,
      "end": 90.0,
      "text": "His poli tsai, which means police t-shirt."
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "start": 90.0,
      "end": 92.84,
      "text": "This one says lover and not to forget about BDSM,"
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "start": 92.84,
      "end": 95.32,
      "text": "which stands for business development, sales and marketing."
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "start": 95.32,
      "end": 96.16,
      "text": "You perv."
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "start": 96.16,
      "end": 98.2,
      "text": "The third visual hook is quite simply"
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "start": 98.2,
      "end": 99.68,
      "text": "your microphone or your gear."
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "start": 99.68,
      "end": 101.6,
      "text": "Sometimes I wear my pink fluffy mic"
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "start": 101.6,
      "end": 103.28,
      "text": "and sometimes my blue fluffy mic."
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "start": 103.28,
      "end": 105.72,
      "text": "Another great example is this one by Subway Takes,"
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "start": 105.72,
      "end": 108.16,
      "text": "where the mic is attached to a subway card."
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "start": 108.16,
      "end": 109.0,
      "text": "Who for you?"
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "start": 109.0,
      "end": 109.84,
      "text": "100% disagree."
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "start": 109.84,
      "end": 111.72,
      "text": "Providing you walk a lot."
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "start": 111.72,
      "end": 113.28,
      "text": "Or this one by Liana Ava,"
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "start": 113.28,
      "end": 115.08,
      "text": "who comments on fashion using"
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "start": 115.08,
      "end": 117.08,
      "text": "what looks like a call center microphone."
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "start": 117.08,
      "end": 118.0,
      "text": "Cleo Camp."
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "start": 118.0,
      "end": 119.04,
      "text": "Hi, I'm Cleo."
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "start": 119.04,
      "end": 121.12,
      "text": "And she designed this piece."
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "start": 121.12,
      "end": 122.88,
      "text": "And this is why it is great."
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "start": 122.88,
      "end": 123.72,
      "text": "I actually bought three."
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "start": 123.72,
      "end": 125.68,
      "text": "Next up, the angle you film from"
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "start": 125.68,
      "end": 127.12,
      "text": "can also be a visual hook."
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "start": 127.12,
      "end": 129.28,
      "text": "Filming from above, below, or from the side"
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "start": 129.28,
      "end": 130.88,
      "text": "breaks patterns for your viewers."
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "start": 130.88,
      "end": 132.52,
      "text": "Just take a look at this YouTube channel"
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "start": 132.52,
      "end": 133.88,
      "text": "called Fashion Neurosis,"
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "start": 133.88,
      "end": 135.64,
      "text": "where Bella Freud interviews people"
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "start": 135.64,
      "end": 138.32,
      "text": "in a laying down therapy-like setting."
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "start": 138.32,
      "end": 139.16,
      "text": "And yes, that's right."
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "start": 139.16,
      "end": 141.56,
      "text": "Bella Freud is Sigmund Freud's great-granddaughter."
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "start": 141.56,
      "end": 143.28,
      "text": "Just take a look at this session with Lord."
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "start": 143.28,
      "end": 146.04,
      "text": "Welcome to Fashion Neurosis, Lord."
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "start": 146.04,
      "end": 147.44,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "start": 147.44,
      "end": 149.76,
      "text": "Can you tell me what clothes you're wearing today"
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "start": 149.76,
      "end": 151.36,
      "text": "and why you chose them?"
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "start": 151.36,
      "end": 156.16,
      "text": "I'm wearing this old Yogi blazer"
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "start": 156.16,
      "end": 157.44,
      "text": "that I really love."
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "start": 157.44,
      "end": 159.8,
      "text": "I'm wearing old Margiela trousers."
    },
    {
      "id": 83,
      "start": 159.8,
      "end": 161.92,
      "text": "And the last visual hook is to do something"
    },
    {
      "id": 84,
      "start": 161.92,
      "end": 163.64,
      "text": "with your hands while you film."
    },
    {
      "id": 85,
      "start": 163.64,
      "end": 165.4,
      "text": "It could be holding a drink like this."
    },
    {
      "id": 86,
      "start": 165.4,
      "end": 167.6,
      "text": "It could be preparing some food or some tea."
    },
    {
      "id": 87,
      "start": 167.6,
      "end": 171.68,
      "text": "Or why not do some crafts while you talk?"
    },
    {
      "id": 88,
      "start": 171.68,
      "end": 173.76,
      "text": "I love this example by Alex on a budget"
    },
    {
      "id": 89,
      "start": 173.76,
      "end": 175.24,
      "text": "where she peels a grapefruit."
    },
    {
      "id": 90,
      "start": 175.24,
      "end": 177.12,
      "text": "It's so random, but it hooks you."
    },
    {
      "id": 91,
      "start": 177.12,
      "end": 178.4,
      "text": "But I'm approaching the 30s."
    },
    {
      "id": 92,
      "start": 178.4,
      "end": 179.56,
      "text": "I have very little patience"
    },
    {
      "id": 93,
      "start": 179.56,
      "end": 181.36,
      "text": "and I don't care about a lot of stuff."
    },
    {
      "id": 94,
      "start": 181.36,
      "end": 183.76,
      "text": "It's for that exact reason that creators on TikTok"
    },
    {
      "id": 95,
      "start": 183.76,
      "end": 185.68,
      "text": "do their makeup while they do storytime."
    },
    {
      "id": 96,
      "start": 185.68,
      "end": 188.24,
      "text": "Things my ex-boyfriend did and I still stayed."
    },
    {
      "id": 97,
      "start": 188.24,
      "end": 189.2,
      "text": "You get the point."
    },
    {
      "id": 98,
      "start": 189.2,
      "end": 192.52,
      "text": "Now, remember, a visual hook can be small or big,"
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "start": 192.52,
      "end": 194.44,
      "text": "but if you manage to stay consistent with it,"
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "start": 194.44,
      "end": 196.64,
      "text": "your viewers will know it's your video"
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "start": 196.64,
      "end": 198.2,
      "text": "before they even hear you talk."
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "start": 198.2,
      "end": 199.68,
      "text": "And that's exactly what you want."
    },
    {
      "id": 103,
      "start": 199.68,
      "end": 201.8,
      "text": "Which of these visual hooks will you be trying?"
    },
    {
      "id": 104,
      "start": 201.8,
      "end": 202.92,
      "text": "And is there a visual hook"
    },
    {
      "id": 105,
      "start": 202.92,
      "end": 204.64,
      "text": "that's worked pretty well for you?"
    },
    {
      "id": 106,
      "start": 204.64,
      "end": 205.96,
      "text": "Feel free to share it below"
    },
    {
      "id": 107,
      "start": 205.96,
      "end": 207.32,
      "text": "and don't forget to subscribe"
    },
    {
      "id": 108,
      "start": 207.32,
      "end": 210.56,
      "text": "if you want more on how to use video to grow your business"
    },
    {
      "id": 109,
      "start": 210.56,
      "end": 212.44,
      "text": "in a way that doesn't burn you out."
    },
    {
      "id": 110,
      "start": 212.44,
      "end": 213.28,
      "text": "See you soon."
    }
  ]
}